{"author_id":"DEMO-AUTHOR-05","content_sha256":"c53cf37d0b95a6a8c00bc8d533d4d48becb322f344b89be596e92cc1519fa928","context":{"genre":"大女主现实向短篇","prohibited_shortcuts":["突然开挂","反派无条件认错","无代价胜利"],"title":"叶知澜：一份被覆盖的版本提交记录"},"dataset_version":"novel-demo-data-v0.1.0","demo":true,"demo_marker":"DEMO_SYNTHETIC_NOT_REAL_WORLD_EVIDENCE","document_id":"DEMO-DOCUMENT-009","eval_id":"EVAL-013","eval_version":"novel-gold-demo-v0.1.0","isolation_assertion":"author_and_work_absent_from_sft_and_preference","prompt":"根据标题《叶知澜：一份被覆盖的版本提交记录》完成evidence_chain任务。答案应保持现实因果、女性主体性和证据可复核性。","reference_answer":"最难的不是找到线索,而是证明线索没有被她自己误读。她请来维护开源工具的匿名玩家,两人把纸面记录、设备日志和现场口述分开核验。第一次交叉比对失败后,她主动推翻自己的假设;第二次复核时,三个彼此独立的时间点终于闭合。就在她准备提交报告时,对方抢先发布声明,把她描述成因私人恩怨报复组织的人。她短暂犹豫,却没有删除任何原始文件。","rights_record_id":"DEMO-RIGHTS-009","rubric":{"dimensions":["causal_coherence","character_agency","evidence_grounding","style_control"],"pass_score":16,"score_range":[1,5]},"sample_id":"EVAL-013","shard_id":"evaluation-isolated-00000","source_author_id":"DEMO-AUTHOR-05","source_id":"DEMO-SOURCE-009","source_work_id":"DEMO-WORK-009","split":"evaluation","task_type":"evidence_chain","work_id":"DEMO-WORK-009"}
{"author_id":"DEMO-AUTHOR-05","content_sha256":"b8f6647c21a4b1114c417daadbf961bc4e8abf68aed32436b0f303af21c9dccd","context":{"genre":"大女主现实向短篇","prohibited_shortcuts":["突然开挂","反派无条件认错","无代价胜利"],"title":"温如霜：一只带有修补痕迹的青铜匣"},"dataset_version":"novel-demo-data-v0.1.0","demo":true,"demo_marker":"DEMO_SYNTHETIC_NOT_REAL_WORLD_EVIDENCE","document_id":"DEMO-DOCUMENT-010","eval_id":"EVAL-014","eval_version":"novel-gold-demo-v0.1.0","isolation_assertion":"author_and_work_absent_from_sft_and_preference","prompt":"根据标题《温如霜：一只带有修补痕迹的青铜匣》完成conflict_escalation任务。答案应保持现实因果、女性主体性和证据可复核性。","reference_answer":"转折发生在公开质询当天:她证明真品上的修补恰恰记录了被抹去的女性工匠。温如霜没有用情绪反击,而是依次展示来源、处理步骤和可以由第三方重复的验证方法。曾经沉默的人开始补充证词,原本被推到台前承担责任的年轻女性也终于获得说明机会。对方试图用一笔优厚和解金结束争议,她拒绝了附带保密条款的条件。","rights_record_id":"DEMO-RIGHTS-010","rubric":{"dimensions":["causal_coherence","character_agency","evidence_grounding","style_control"],"pass_score":16,"score_range":[1,5]},"sample_id":"EVAL-014","shard_id":"evaluation-isolated-00000","source_author_id":"DEMO-AUTHOR-05","source_id":"DEMO-SOURCE-010","source_work_id":"DEMO-WORK-010","split":"evaluation","task_type":"conflict_escalation","work_id":"DEMO-WORK-010"}
{"author_id":"DEMO-AUTHOR-06","content_sha256":"167e081cdc2dbf1eecf0cba666bd92482cc4baa037bfdfce34de0b4824ba4f6c","context":{"genre":"大女主现实向短篇","prohibited_shortcuts":["突然开挂","反派无条件认错","无代价胜利"],"title":"唐映雪：一批检测编号连续跳号的样品"},"dataset_version":"novel-demo-data-v0.1.0","demo":true,"demo_marker":"DEMO_SYNTHETIC_NOT_REAL_WORLD_EVIDENCE","document_id":"DEMO-DOCUMENT-011","eval_id":"EVAL-015","eval_version":"novel-gold-demo-v0.1.0","isolation_assertion":"author_and_work_absent_from_sft_and_preference","prompt":"根据标题《唐映雪：一批检测编号连续跳号的样品》完成costly_resolution任务。答案应保持现实因果、女性主体性和证据可复核性。","reference_answer":"最终,她选择完成全链路召回并建立公开检测编号。事情没有以童话式胜利收尾:她失去一个重要合作机会,也花了数月修复信任。但新的制度开始运转,后来者不必再靠孤勇保存真相。夜色降临时,唐映雪把调查代号从白板上擦掉,只留下最后一句备注:证据不是武器,它首先是一条让普通人能够返回事实的路。","rights_record_id":"DEMO-RIGHTS-011","rubric":{"dimensions":["causal_coherence","character_agency","evidence_grounding","style_control"],"pass_score":16,"score_range":[1,5]},"sample_id":"EVAL-015","shard_id":"evaluation-isolated-00000","source_author_id":"DEMO-AUTHOR-06","source_id":"DEMO-SOURCE-011","source_work_id":"DEMO-WORK-011","split":"evaluation","task_type":"costly_resolution","work_id":"DEMO-WORK-011"}
